How Does the Blockchain Work?	Website	An article written by Michele D'Aliessi on Medium that explains blockchain technology in simple words.
A Gentle Introduction to Blockchain Technology	Website	This article is a gentle introduction to blockchain technology and assumes minimal technical knowledge. It attempts to describe “what it is” rather than “why should I care”.
